[para:diff] [#temp.deduct.type]
[?change]
[:en] Allowance to deduce from the type of a constant template argument.
[:zh_CN] 允许从常量模板实参进行推断。

[?rationale]
[:en] In combination with the ability to declare constant template arguments
with placeholder types, allows partial specializations to decompose from the
type deduced for the constant template argument.
[:zh_CN] 将声明常量模板实参和占位符类型组合起来，允许部分特化式对常量模板实参
所推断的类型进行分解。

[?effect]
[:en] Valid [=CppXIV] code may fail to compile or produce different results in
this revision of [=Cpp].
[:zh_CN] 有效的 [=CppXIV] 代码在 [=Cpp] 的此版本中可能无法编译或产生不同的结果。

[begin:example]
[codeblock]
template <int N> struct A;
template <typename T, T N> int foo(A<N> *) = delete;
void foo(void *);
void bar(A<0> *p) {
  foo(p);           // [:en] ill-formed; previously well-formed \
                    [:zh_CN] 非良构；之前则为良构
}
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]
